    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable, smooth journey without the brand-new price tag. It runs great and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to ask any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
