    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically sound, the vehicle benefits from a recent VANOS system overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing key platform-specific concerns. The engine's individual throttle bodies provide exceptional throttle response, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures maximum traction out of apexes. Finished in Carbon Black over a well-bolstered interior, it retains its factory suspension geometry and staggered 18-inch Style 67 wheels. A purist\u2019s machine with linear power delivery and precise steering feedback.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
