    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care. This car presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a sharp, clean profile with only the minor, honest character marks expected of a well-loved driver. The interior is a highlight: the premium leather seats remain firm and supportive, the dashboard is free of any sun-fading, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014works exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio that shows regular oil changes and proactive belt replacements. We\u2019ve recently fitted a fresh set of all-season tires and performed a full fluid flush, meaning this car is ready for the open road the moment you take the keys. It offers a refined, stable ride that proves you don't need to buy 'mint' to get a high-quality, reliable experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
