    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it's ready for a new adventure. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect if you're looking for a great ride that still has plenty of life left! It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
